小弟係某 gp 到見到個大法<br />
係透過睇 github pr/commit 俾大家睇到間公司有冇 ot <br />
方法好簡單<br />
但係要間公司有 github oss project 先得<br />
<br />
首先入去 github 個 graphql explorer<br />
跟住登入返<br />
然後入以下 graphql query 落去<br />
<pre><code data-type="">query OTJobViewer($owner: String!, $name: String!, $first: Int, $issueOrder: IssueOrder) {
  repository(owner: $owner, name: $name) {
    pullRequests(first: $first, orderBy: $issueOrder) {
      nodes {
        createdAt
        url
      }
    }
  }
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
跟住 入番啲 graphql variable<br />
呢度今次用skygear做例子<br />
因為佢有 oss 個 platform 出來<br />
<pre><code data-type="">{
  &quot;owner&quot;: &quot;SkygearIO&quot;,
  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;skygear-server&quot;,
  &quot;first&quot;: 20,
  &quot;issueOrder&quot;: {
    &quot;field&quot;: &quot;CREATED_AT&quot;,
    &quot;direction&quot;: &quot;DESC&quot;
  }
}</code></pre><br />
